@6120  = ~Abi-Dalzim's Horrid Wilting
(Necromancy) 

Level: 8
Range: Visual range of the caster 
Duration: Instant
Casting Time: 8
Area of Effect: 30-ft. radius
Saving Throw: 1/2

This spell creates violent whorls of magical energy within the area of effect which do grievous harm to all enemies, inflicting 1d8 damage per level of the caster. Affected creatures are allowed a Saving Throw vs. Spell for half damage. This spell is especially devastating to water elementals and plant creatures, who receive a penalty of -2 to their Saving Throws.~
@6121  = ~Black Blade of Disaster
