@6271   = ~Shadow Clone~
@6272   = ~Shadow Clone
Level: 6
School: Illusion
Range: Caster
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: none

This spell creates a rough facsimile of the caster, recognizable though not perfect. (Maybe I'll add a Blur visual effect to the clone.) The shadow clone has the equivalent of 60% of the experience (level, hit dice, skills, etc.) of the original caster, and can replicate some small amount of the caster's magical abilities, able to cast 1st level spells. The shadow clone cannot engage in melee combat or make use of any magical "items" it has equipped.
~
@6273   = ~Misleading Clone~
@6274   = ~Misleading Clone
Level: 7
School: Illusion
Range: Caster
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: none

This spell is cast very quickly, creating a reasonable copy of the caster that can be perceived by all five senses of any onlookers. The clone has the equivalent of 60% of the experience (level, hit dice, skills, etc.) of the caster, and can replicate a moderate amount of the caster's magical abilities, able to cast up to 3rd level spells. The clone cannot engage in melee combat or make use of any magical "items" it has equipped. At the time the clone is created, the caster is rendered invisible for 60 seconds. Onlookers who do not carefully scrutinize the effect might easily believe the clone IS the caster, and the caster may use the distraction to escape or move to some advantageous position.
~
@6275   = ~Simulacrum~
@6276   = ~Simulacrum
Level: 8
School: Illusion
Range: Caster
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 7
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: none

This is an improvement on the Misleading Clone spell. The simulacrum created has 60% of the experience (level, hit dice, skills, etc.) of the caster, but can replicate all of the caster's magical abilities, able to cast any spells that the caster could at the clone's reduced level. The simulacrum also has enough substance and stability to engage in melee combat, but cannot use any magical "items" it has equipped. Simultaneously, the caster is affected by Improved Invisibility, able to move unnnoticed and even attack or cast spells without becoming fully visible.
~

@6277   = ~Project Image~
@6278   = ~Project Image
Level: 9
School: Illusion
Range: Caster
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: none

This powerful spell creates a perfect clone, with 100% of the experience (level, hit dice, skills, etc.) of the caster. The clone is able to cast any spells that the caster can, and has enough substance and stability to engage in melee combat with skill equal to the caster's. Simultaneously, the caster is affected by Improved Invisibility, able to move unnnoticed and even attack or cast spells without becoming fully visible.
~
