This spell creates between one and five missiles of fiery magical energy that dart forth from the wizard's fingertips and unerringly strike their target, which must be a creature of some sort. Each missile inflicts 1d4 points of damage, plus 1d4 points of fire damage (the victim may save vs. Breath to avoid the fire damage). For every 3 extra levels of experience after 1st level, the wizard gains an additional missile - 2 at 4th level, 3 at 7th level, 4 at 10th level, and a maximum of 5 at 13th level.
~
