@7151  = ~Shocking Grasp~
@7152  = ~Shocking Grasp
(Alteration)

Level: 1
Range: Touch
Duration: Special
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: None

When the wizard touches a creature while this spell is in effect, an electrical charge will deal 1d8 points of damage, plus 1 additional point per two levels of the caster (to a maximum of 1d8+5 points of damage, at 10th level.) In addition, the grasp itself does 1d2 fist damage (Strength bonuses apply). The wizard only has one charge, and once an opponent has been touched, the spell's energies have been used. If the wizard misses, the spell is wasted. The wizard has 1 round per level to touch the target creature.
~
@7154  = ~Shocking Grasp

Level: 1
School: Evocation
Range: Personal
Duration: Special
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: Special

When the wizard touches a creature while this spell is in effect, an electrical charge will deal 2d4 points of damage and stun the target for 1 round. If the target makes a successful saving throw vs. spell, he is not stunned. For every two extra experience levels of the caster, the creature will suffer an additional points of damage and roll their saving throw at an increased -1 penalty (to a maximum of 2d4+4 damage and a -4 saving throw penalty, at 9th level). The spell expires once the caster makes a successful melee attack or after 1 turn has passed. The wizard gains a +4 bonus to hit the target.
~
@7161  = ~Drowse~
@7162  = ~Drowse
(Enchantment/Charm)

Level: 1
Range: 60 ft.
Duration: 5 rounds
Casting Time: 1 
Area of Effect: 30-ft. radius
Saving Throw: Neg.

When a wizard casts this spell, <PRO_HESHE> causes slumber to come upon one enemy (other than undead and certain other creatures specifically excluded from the spell's effects). The creature must make a saving throw vs. Spells or fall asleep. Attacks against sleeping opponents never miss.

If the sleeping creature takes damage, <PRO_HESHE> will slowly wake up over the course of 1 round. Additionally, once a creature has been put to sleep by this spell, that being cannot be affected by another casting of the spell for 8 hours.
~
@7163  = ~Sleep~
@7164  = ~Sleep
(Enchantment/Charm)

Level: 2
Range: 60 ft.
Duration: 5 rounds
Casting Time: 1 
Area of Effect: 30-ft. radius
Saving Throw: Neg.

When a wizard casts this spell, <PRO_HESHE> causes a comatose slumber to come upon one or more enemies within a 30-ft. radius (other than undead and certain other creatures specifically excluded from the spell's effects). Creatures in the area of effect must make a saving throw vs. Spells with a -3 penalty or fall asleep. Monsters with 5 Hit Dice or more are unaffected. Attacks against sleeping opponents never miss.

If a sleeping creature takes damage, they will slowly wake up over the course of 1 round. Additionally, once a creature has been put to sleep by this spell, that being cannot be affected by another casting of the spell for 8 hours.
~
